property.value: Hold A to walk left or D to walk right. You can review the keyboard controls in the bottom left corner of the screen.|You can also see contextual options for the left and right mouse buttons in the bottom right corner of the screen.

property.name: text
property.value: After jumping with W, hold towards a wall to grab onto it. Once you have grabbed the wall, you can press W to jump again. By repeating this process, you can climb vertical walls of any height!

property.name: text
property.value: Press S to curl up into a ball, then use A or D to roll. While in this state, you can fit into smaller spaces. Rolling is also faster than walking. Press W to stand back up.
